Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.37,0:01:53.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{It was an emergency ration\Nfor true emergencies}dành cho những tình cảnh ngặt nghèo nhất!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.49,0:01:56.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{that was saved for\Nthe last of the last resorts.}Đó vốn là khẩu phần của ta\Ntrong trường hợp khẩn cấp.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:01.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{All I'm asking is who ate this.}Tôi hỏi ai đã ăn chỗ đồ ăn đó.
