Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:05.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{Spike, by perchance, was it you?}Spike, đừng nói là cậu nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.82,0:02:09.78,Main,combine,0,0,0,,{If I was the culprit, I wouldn't leave\Nthe empty box lying around like that.}Nếu tôi là thủ phạm,\Ntôi sẽ không để cái hộp trống nằm lung tung như thế.
