Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:32.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{Can you go get some food?}Cô đi tìm đồ ăn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:36.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{What?}Gì cơ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:38.99,Main,combine,0,0,0,,{I suddenly feel... a stabbing pain...}Đột ngột... đau nhói.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:40.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{What are you trying to pull?}Giở trò gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:48.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{This expired a year ago...}Thứ này hết hạn một năm trước rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm glad I didn't eat it.}Mừng là mình chưa ăn nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{Serves you right. This is divine retribution!}Trả giá đi nhé. Bị quả báo đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:04:59.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{Let's get to it...}Làm việc thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:12.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{Whatcha gonna do?}Ta nên làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:15.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ed will help, too!}Ed cũng sẽ giúp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:22.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{We're fine here, so go outside\Nand find us some food.}Ở đây không sao. Em ra ngoài tìm đồ ăn đi.
