Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.29,Main,split,0,0,0,,{A cowboy?}Cô là cao bồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:35.80,Main,split,0,0,0,,{We're gonna check out your trunk.}Chúng tôi cũng cần kiểm tra xe cô.
