Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:52.27,Default - Alt,split,0,0,0,,{Now put your hands on the ground! Hurry up!}Đặt tay xuống đất. Nhanh lên!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.01,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Let go of me!}Thả tôi ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:57.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{Food, food, do you have any?}Đồ ăn, đồ ăn\NCó gì ăn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:09:00.85,Main,combine,0,0,0,,{Oh, you don't? Oh, you do?}Không có gì ăn ư? Có gì ăn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{Boy, am I hungry...}Trời ơi, đói quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:17.16,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Meanie!}Xấu tính quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:18.42,Main,split,0,0,0,,{What?}Gì cơ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:19.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{Gimme!}Đưa cho cháu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:21.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{Gimme something!}Cho cháu một miếng!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:23.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{Dammit, stop hanging all over me!}Đủ rồi! Đừng bám víu chú nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:25.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:29.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{I won't let you tell me you\Nforgot who I am, Domino!}Đừng nghĩ tao sẽ để mày nói\Nrằng mày đã quên tao, Domino!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:30.73,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Let's see... [10 frames]}Xem nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.10,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Come on! Remember, dammit!}Chết tiệt, cố nhớ đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:35.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm the younger of the Shaft brothers\Nthat bought mushrooms from you!}Tao là em út trong đám anh em nhà Shaft.\NTao đã mua nấm của mày!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:37.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{I really can't recall...}Tôi thật sự không nhớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:43.07,Main,combine,0,0,0,,{You do want to know why I drag an\Nempty coffin around like this, don't you?}Muốn biết tại sao tao lại kéo\N một cái quan tài rỗng đi quanh thế này không?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.12,Main,split,0,0,0,,{It's because...}Là vì...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:48.08,Main,split,0,0,0,,{I'm going to go home after\Nputting your corpse inside—}tao sẽ mang nó về nhà\N sau khi bỏ xác mày vào—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:53.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{Pieces... All in pieces!}Tan tành. Tan tành thành trăm mảnh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:54.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{What was what to who?}Anh nói gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:59.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{My big bro ate a mushroom\Nhe bought from you}Anh hai tao đã ăn một cây nấm mua của mày
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:02.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{and laughed and laughed\Nand twisted his intestines to death!}rồi cười suốt ngày,\Nvà sao đó chết vì xoắn ruột.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:05.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{A happy way to die.}Chết thật thanh thản.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{Shut up!}Câm mồm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.57,0:10:08.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{Speaking of which, it's all your fault!}Tất cả là tại mày!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:10.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{That's what I call an unjust resentment!}Tôi giúp người mà phải lãnh hậu quả này à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:12.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ed is hungry, too!}Ed đói quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:14.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{Take this!}Đỡ này!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:19.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{Wait, you bastard! Dammit!}Đợi đã, thằng khốn! Chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:21.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{Food!}Đồ ăn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:26.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{Aah! Don't, Ein! We have to share!}Này, thôi đi Ein!\NTa phải chia sẻ với mọi người.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:36.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ein?}Ein?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:44.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{Bad mushroom?}Nấm hư rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:06.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{This for real?}Cái này là thật ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:16.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{Delicious!}Ngon quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:28.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{This really can't be happening.}Không thể nào.\NChuyện như thế này không thể xảy ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:36.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{Really... This really has no way of happening.}Không thể nào. Thôi nào. Sao nó lại ở đây?
Comment: 1,0:12:53.15,0:12:54.57,Main,from_ocr,0,0,0,,{\an8}CÓ NGƯỜI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:15.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey... You know, the world\Nreally is a great place...}Tụi mày biết không,\Nthế giới thật tuyệt vời.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:21.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{Did I just say something?}Mình vừa nói gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:30.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey, mister.}Này cậu chủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:36.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{This is a stairway to heaven.\NYou know that, right?}Đây là cầu thang lên thiên đường.\NCậu biết mà, phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:39.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{An obnoxious little frog...}Chú ếch nhỏ phiền hà.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.79,0:13:45.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{See if I care. I warned you! [original: "I don't care anymore. I warned you!"]}Đừng nói là tôi không cảnh báo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:16.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, yeah, that's it.}Ừ, đúng rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:20.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{I now know the secrets of the universe.}Giờ tao đã biết bí mật của vũ trụ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:25.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{By the way...}Nhân tiện,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:27.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{who was I?}tao là ai vậy chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:31.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{So these mushrooms are\Ninedible after all...}Kết luận là ta không thể ăn thứ nấm này.
Comment: 1,0:14:34.12,0:14:37.17,Main,from_ocr,0,0,0,,BIG SHOT\NCHƯƠNG TRÌNH DÀNH CHO THỢ SĂN TIỀN THƯỞNG
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:40.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, as you can tell, it's time for\Nanother episode of Big Shot!}{\i0}{\i1}Lại là chương trình {\i0}Big Shot {\i1}đây!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:43.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{and more bounties this week!}{\i0}{\i1}Tuần này thông tin về tiền thưởng{\i0}\N{\i1}lan nhanh như lửa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, batting first for us today...}{\i0}{\an8}{\i1}Hôm nay ai là kẻ đầu tiên?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.99,0:14:47.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{...is this man, Domino Walker.}{\i0}{\an8}{\i1}Người này, Domino Walker.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:50.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{selling illegal mushrooms.}{\i0}{\an8}{\i1}Hắn bị truy nã vì bán nấm bất hợp pháp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:52.93,Main,split,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The bounty is a conservative 1.2 mil.}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:52.93,Default - Alt,split,0,0,0,,{Nya! That's the guy we just saw!}Là người chúng ta vừa gặp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:55.25,Main,split,0,0,0,,{That's cowgirl, Ein.}Ein, đến lúc làm cô gái cao bồi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.25,0:14:58.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{We earn money, and buy food!}Ta sẽ kiếm tiền và mua đồ ăn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:01.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ein, you're a cow-woofwoof!}Ein, em là chó cao bồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.19,0:15:10.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{Here we go!}Lên đường thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:11.68,Main,split,0,0,0,,{One!}Một!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:12.49,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Two!}Hai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:13.24,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Five!}Năm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:14.09,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Four!}Bốn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:15.66,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Hello!}Xin chào!
Comment: 1,0:15:23.09,0:15:23.92,Main,from_ocr,0,0,0,,CẢNH SÁT
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:26.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey, don't underestimate the police!}{\i1}Này! Đừng giỡn mặt với tôi nữa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:28.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{I really don't know anything!}Tôi đã nói tôi không biết gì cả!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:31.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{Then why did you have a strange kid\Nand a dog in the trunk of your car?!}Sao có một đứa trẻ và một con chó\Ntrong cốp xe? Chưa từng gặp chúng ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:35.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hello... Yes?}A lô?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:39.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh, it's you, Sally.\NReally... You're so hopeless...}À, là em à, Sally! Em thật hết thuốc chữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:42.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{I told you so many times\Nnot to call me at work...}Anh đã nói đừng gọi cho anh vào giờ làm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:49.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{And? Yeah yeah, and that's it?}Được rồi. Thì sao? Vậy thôi sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:51.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{ way\Nwhen I said "that's it?"...}{\i0}Không, anh không có ý như thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:55.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, yeah, like that. I love you, Sally.}Ừ, đúng vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:57.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{Got it. Tonight at 7 it is. Bye-bye!}Hiểu rồi. Tối nay lúc 7:00. Tạm biệt em!
Comment: 1,0:15:58.87,0:15:59.88,Main,from_ocr,0,0,0,,Sao cơ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:03.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:10.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{What's wrong, young'un?\NLookin' like that...}Sao vậy, chàng trai trẻ? Sao u sầu thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{Did your woman run off without you?}Bị bồ đá hay sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:13.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{What to say...}Tôi đoán thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:16.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{None of your business, old geezers.}Không phải việc của mấy ông,\Nmấy lão già kỳ quái.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:26.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh, man... that's for eating all at once.}Anh ăn nhanh quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:29.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{They say when you're in a hurry, go around.}Người ta nói\Nđi vội đi vàng là quàng phải dây đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:30.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{Is that right?}Phải không vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:39.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{He's not here...}Chú ấy không ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:46.37,Main,,0,0,0,,{Aah! That hit-and-run ship!}Con tàu đã tông ta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:56.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm sure they never even dreamed\Nthat I was raising these in here.}Không ai có thể ngờ\Nlà mình trồng những thứ này ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:16:59.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{This one's bad.}Cái này không tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:04.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{Well, making an emergency landing here\Nwas the only miscalculation I had.}Mình đã không định\Nhạ cánh khẩn cấp ở đây nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:05.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{Were you surprised?}Làm chú giật mình à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:07.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{I was.}Đúng vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.40,Main,split,0,0,0,,{What the hell are you guys?}Mày là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:10.67,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Why are you here?}Sao chú lại ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:14.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{That's my line! How did you\Nget in here in the first place?}Tao nói câu đó mới phải!\NSao mày vào được đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:15.36,Main,split,0,0,0,,{The door was open.}Cửa mở mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:15.36,Default - Alt,split,0,0,0,,{Is that so?! [extra lead-in]}Gì cơ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:18.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{Culprit of the hit-and-run,\Nprepare to get arrested!}Chú bị bắt rồi, Chú Tông Rồi Bỏ Trốn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:20.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{Stink bug gas!}Khí bọ xít!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:29.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{Wait, wait, wait!}Chờ đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:22.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{Don't think that you can get away from me!}Mày tưởng có thể thoát ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:33.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{Don't get in my way!}Đó là tiền thưởng của tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:01.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ein! Growl!}Ein! Đuổi theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:09.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{C-Come on! Let go of me!}Này! Thả ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:33.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{Boo!}Hù!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:49.01,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Gotcha!}Bắt được rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:49.68,Main,split,0,0,0,,{W-Wait...}Đợi đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:53.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{Th-These mushrooms are\Nworth 100,000 each.}Những cây nấm này trị giá 100.000 mỗi cây.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:55.99,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Let me go, and I'll give them to you.}Thả chú đi thì chú cho cháu hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:56.65,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Why?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:59.04,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Think about which one is worth more.}Nghĩ xem cái nào đáng giá hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:19:59.90,Main,split,0,0,0,,{I dunno.}Cháu không biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:01.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{A-Are you an idiot?! [9 frames]}Sao mày ngốc vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:04.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{Take the mushrooms!}Lấy nấm đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:06.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{Okay!}Được rồi!
